Pernambuco State League 1998

Participants:

1o de Maio (Petrolina)
Cabense (Cabo)
Central (Caruaru)
Ferroviário (Serra Talhada)
Flamengo (Arcoverde)
Náutico (Recife)
Petrolândia (Petrolândia)
Porto (Caruaru)
Recife (Recife)
Santa Cruz (Recife)
Sport (Recife)
Vitória (Vitória de Santo Antão)

FIRST PHASE

Top 8 qualify to the Second Phase.  Bottom 4 go to "Repescagem".  Winner
of the first phase qualifies to the Final Phase.

A win is worth 3 points, a draw with goals scored is worth 2 and a draw
without any goals is worth 1.

Round 1
[Jan 25]
Sport         4-0   Petrolândia
Náutico       3-0   Vitória
Santa Cruz    2-1   1o de Maio
Porto         2-0   Central
Cabense       1-1   Flamengo
Recife        0-0   Ferroviário

