Since Sport was already qualified for final, second team decided by combined
table.

Combined Table (1st, 2nd and 3rd Phases):

 1.Sport               23 20  1/2  0  62- 9   64 
 2.Porto               23 11  7/0  5  43-28   47
 3.Náutico             23 13  2/2  6  46-26   45
 4.Santa Cruz          23  8  6/2  7  32-26   38
 5.Ferroviário         23  8  3/2 10  29-41   32

Porto due to better championship record qualifies to the Final Phase.

FINAL PHASE
If Sport wins or draws the first game of the Final Phase, Sport is the champion.
If Porto wins the game, another match will be disputed.

FINAL
[Jun 7]
Sport         2-0   Porto

Sport Club do Recife wins the 1998 Pernambuco state championship


